Supabase-backed admin publishing and advertising remain optional later phases, not part of this numbered sequence.

The detailed session-by-session implementation roadmap for this sequence is maintained as a prompt pack in `docs/website-overhaul/MARI-MEDIA-COMPASS-CURSOR-OVERHAUL-PROMPT-PACK.md`. That document is an implementation roadmap and session guide, not a Cursor rule; it does not carry rule authority and must not conflict with this file. If it ever appears to conflict, this rule wins and the conflict should be flagged rather than silently resolved.
